OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FSome business owners have opted to
OL,7,Fshut early and give their staff a half-
OL,8,Fday to watch England tonight. GMB
OL,9,Fspoke to business owners about the
OL,10,Fpros and cons of letting workers head
OL,11,Foff to the pub before 5pm
OL,13,FMillions of extra pints are expected
OL,14,Fto be sold in pubs on Wednesday as
OL,15,FEngland face DR Congo ` while the
OL,16,Fnumber of workers calling in sick is
OL,17,Fpredicted to increase.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
