FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FFour million extra pints are set to be
OL,7,Fpoured on Wednesday, which would be a
OL,8,F#20 million boost to pubs across the
OL,9,FUK, according to estimates from the
OL,10,FBritish Beer and Pub Association.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, some employers are allowing
OL,13,Fstaff to work flexible hours, closing
OL,14,Fearly or are bringing TVs into
OL,15,Fworkplaces ahead of the 5pm kick-off.
OL,17,FBut Alan Price, chief executive of
OL,18,FBrightHR, still expects there to be a
OL,19,Frise in "sickness" on Wednesday and
OL,20,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
