FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FSome fans online have joked they will
OL,7,Fbe attending a doctor's appointment
OL,8,Fwithout necessarily clarifying that
OL,9,Fthe doctor in question is DR Congo.
OL,11,FOasis frontman Liam Gallagher posted
OL,12,Fon X after the debate asking, 'Did
OL,13,FRavir just say England fans who are
OL,14,Fworking should be allowed to **** off
OL,15,Fhome early'
OL,17,FEngland play DR Congo in Atlanta for
OL,18,Fthe first round of the knockout stages
OL,19,Fon Wednesday at 5pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FIt comes after previous England games
OL,7,Fwere held at 9pm or 10pm BST, meaning
OL,8,Fchildren are also more likely to be
OL,9,Fable to watch the match well ahead of
OL,10,Fbedtime.
OL,12,FAndy Tighe, chief strategy officer at
OL,13,Fthe British Beer and Pub Association,
OL,14,Fsaid the game will be "a welcome boost
OL,15,Fto trade".
OL,17,FHe said: "We're very excited, it's a
OL,18,Fgreat time, and because it's the first
OL,19,Fknockout round as well it's make or
OL,20,Fbreak, so there's a lot riding on it.
OL,26,@vD@WOUwD@IO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,F"We are expecting the pubs to be busy.
OL,7,FAll in all, it should be a very
OL,8,Fpositive evening for pubs, we're very
OL,9,Fexcited."
OL,11,FHe added: "We've definitely seen some
OL,12,Fbig upticks across the country in pubs
OL,13,Ffor the previous games as well.
OL,15,F"We've seen in previous tournaments
OL,16,Fthat as the tournament progresses, the
OL,17,Flevel of interest only increases."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]sD@KOUwD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
