PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FMr Tighe said margins in pubs have
OL,7,Fbeen "squeezed and squeezed and
OL,8,Fsqueezed", so "occasions like this are
OL,9,Fas important as ever".
OL,11,FHe added: "It will be a welcome boost
OL,12,Fto trade at this time."
OL,14,FMr Price, from BrightHR ` which
OL,15,Fprovides HR software and advice and
OL,16,Fworks with 68,000 small businesses in
OL,17,Fthe UK ` said they have already seen a
OL,18,F5% increase in employees that have
OL,19,Fbooked time off from their systems.
OL,26,@oD@FOUpD@IO]pD@OOUqD@UO]sD@KOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
