OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FHe added: "Some employers are letting
OL,7,Fstaff come in earlier so they can
OL,8,Fleave early, we've had calls saying
OL,9,F'can we show it on TV in work', some
OL,10,Femployers are bringing TV monitors in.
OL,12,F"Some people are working flexi, say
OL,13,Fyou're processing mortgage
OL,14,Fapplications, that isn't something
OL,15,Fthat has to be done then, so some
OL,16,Femployers are being flexible.
OL,18,F"Some businesses are closing early."
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUzD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
