OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FMr Price also said he thinks there
OL,7,Fwill be an increase in workers calling
OL,8,Fin sick, adding he believes there will
OL,9,Fbe more sick calls on Thursday rather
OL,10,Fthan Wednesday.
OL,12,FHe said: "I think there will be more
OL,13,Fon Thursday; a lot of employers will
OL,14,Fhave been flexible on Wednesday or had
OL,15,Fit on in the workplace, so we will see
OL,16,Fmore sickness the day after."
OL,18,FGermany is out of the World Cup.
OL,19,FBrazil was pushed to the edge by Japan
OL,20,Fand the Netherlands was sent packing.
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
