OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FFootball's traditional superpowers
OL,7,Fhave been rattled by a combination of
OL,8,Ffearless underdogs and emerging forces
OL,9,Fshaking things up.
OL,11,FAnd England coach Thomas Tuchel has no
OL,12,Fissue with it at all.
OL,14,F"I think it can calm us down in a
OL,15,Fway," he told a press conference.
OL,16,F"It's just narrow margins. It's just
OL,17,Ftight football matches, and it helps
OL,18,Fus not to overexpect.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@EOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,F"It helps to put it in the right
OL,7,Fframework what is happening in this
OL,8,FWorld Cup and in world football," he
OL,9,Fsaid ahead of England's round of 32
OL,10,Fgame against Congo in Atlanta on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FEngland is the overwhelming favourite
OL,14,Fto advance against a team that is
OL,15,Fplaying in the knockouts for the first
OL,16,Ftime and is in its first World Cup
OL,17,Fsince 1974.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782901111
OL,3,CRise in workplace 'sickness' expected
OL,4,Cas England prepare to face DR Congo
OL,6,FBut Tuchel, whose team was criticised
OL,7,Fafter its goalless draw with Ghana in
OL,8,Fthe group stage, said the gap is
OL,9,Fclosing in international football.
OL,11,F"It's difficult for any team to break
OL,12,Fteams down, especially when you arrive
OL,13,Fas a favourite. Especially when you
OL,14,Fface teams who have nothing to lose,"
OL,15,FTuchel said.
OL,17,F"For me and for us it almost helps us
OL,18,Fto calm our minds, to accept the
OL,19,Fsituation, and make the most of it."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@eO]yD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
